# SPA Rewrite Rules — Cloudflare Pages
# Rute SPA di-rewrite ke index.html dengan status 200 (bukan 404)
# Static files (robots.txt, sitemap.xml, dll) tetap di-serve langsung dari public/

/login              /index.html   200
/register           /index.html   200
/forgot-password    /index.html   200
/auth/*             /index.html   200
/dashboard/*        /index.html   200
/admin/*            /index.html   200
